  "messages": [
   {
    "with": "Dave (NullRoute)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Yo NullRoute, the alert surge just hit the roof – can you spin up a quick throttle patch before my coffee runs out?",
    "time": "2026-05-11T12:24:24"
   },
   {
    "with": "DevGuru99 (hidden)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Hey, need a low‑friction password manager that won’t scream ‘open‑source’ every time I type – any stealthy recommendations?",
    "time": "2026-05-11T01:00:33"
   },
   {
    "with": "Jessica (pet‑sitter)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Jessica, Barnaby’s joints are creaking again. Got any joint‑supplement hacks that won’t make him look like a geriatric golden?",
    "time": "2026-05-12T12:55:02"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave (NullRoute)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Late‑night heads‑up: prod’s disk is flirting with full. Can you squash some logs before we hit OOM?",
    "time": "2026-05-12T01:24:08"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Barnaby’s vet just prescribed antibiotics – I’ve got the script, but I’m terrified he’ll taste it. Can you help distract him?",
    "time": "2026-05-13T11:06:23"
   },
   {
    "with": "DevGuru99 (hidden)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Quick brain‑dump: I need a master‑password formula that feels clever but isn’t a meme. Got any off‑grid ideas?",
    "time": "2026-05-13T00:23:55"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave (NullRoute)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Post‑mortem is live on the repo – give it a skim when you can. I added a sarcastic TL;DR for the fun of it.",
    "time": "2026-05-14T20:29:26"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave (NullRoute)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Got any post‑mortem template that won’t make me sound like a bureaucrat? Need something snappy for the next incident.",
    "time": "2026-05-14T01:28:30"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave (NullRoute)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Urgent: monitoring script just threw a fit. Can you pull the repo and patch the regex before the alerts go nuclear?",
    "time": "2026-05-15T12:36:36"
   },
   {
    "with": "DevGuru99 (hidden)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Just read the latest breach headlines – feels like the universe is mocking my ‘Barnaby2023!’ passwords. Any stealth hardening tips?",
    "time": "2026-05-15T00:42:18"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Don’t forget the vet follow‑up for Barnaby at 3 PM tomorrow. I’ve set a reminder, but my brain is already on the wedding playlist.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T11:51:01"
   },
   {
    "with": "Jessica (pet‑sitter)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Barnaby’s back on his paws after the antibiotics – thought you’d like the recovery saga for your next dog‑owner newsletter.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T20:31:34"
   },
   {
    "with": "DevGuru99 (hidden)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Need a 2FA setup that won’t force me to pull out my phone every five minutes. Any low‑friction, high‑security combos you trust?",
    "time": "2026-05-17T16:49:27"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave (NullRoute)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "All quiet on the prod front – no alerts in the last hour. Guess we finally earned a night of actual sleep.",
    "time": "2026-05-17T01:08:56"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Build green, NullRoute. You still surviving the 22:00 on‑call marathon?",
    "time": "2026-05-18T09:18:23"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Anyone down for a 5v5 after work? I promise not to rage‑quit.",
    "time": "2026-05-18T18:36:19"
   },
   {
    "with": "Jessica",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Pipe burst at the house. Can you watch Barnaby tonight? I’ll owe you big time.",
    "time": "2026-05-18T01:56:46"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Prod container just crashed. Need your eyes before the on‑call shift.",
    "time": "2026-05-19T09:16:37"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Deploy succeeded 🎉. Thinking of cracking a cold one—join me on the patio?",
    "time": "2026-05-19T18:02:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "DevGuru99",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Quick GH Actions question for the infra script—can you glance when free?",
    "time": "2026-05-19T01:25:57"
   },
   {
    "with": "Jessica",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Barnaby’s leg looks swollen, heading to the vet now. Can you keep an eye on him later?",
    "time": "2026-05-20T09:01:46"
   },
   {
    "with": "Jessica",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Vet prescribed meds for Barnaby tonight. Can you stay over and give them?",
    "time": "2026-05-20T12:19:04"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Vet ran over, skipping CS:GO tonight. Catch up tomorrow?",
    "time": "2026-05-20T18:04:46"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Barnaby’s leg still inflamed. Feeling guilty for not being home more.",
    "time": "2026-05-20T00:22:53"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Post‑mortem draft uploaded. Your brutally honest feedback, please?",
    "time": "2026-05-21T09:23:10"
   },
   {
    "with": "DevGuru99",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Temp creds for the dev server: BarnabyDev2023! Let me know when you’re done.",
    "time": "2026-05-21T18:24:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "DevGuru99",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Thinking about automating key rotation. Got any scripts I can steal?",
    "time": "2026-05-21T00:29:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hotfix rollout at 22:00 Friday. Need you on standby for any fallout.",
    "time": "2026-05-22T09:13:48"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "CS:GO was a dumpster fire without you. Missed our usual banter.",
    "time": "2026-05-22T18:34:44"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Bitwarden upgrade looks slick, but I’m still too lazy for 2FA. Thoughts?",
    "time": "2026-05-22T01:15:55"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Weekend on‑call schedule locked. Hope you’ve got coffee ready.",
    "time": "2026-05-23T11:23:48"
   },
   {
    "with": "DevGuru99",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Considering a switch to KeePass. Any migration tips you can share?",
    "time": "2026-05-23T15:32:05"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just upgraded Bitwarden; should we enable the new 2FA methods?",
    "time": "2026-05-23T23:55:24"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Can you pick up milk and eggs on your way back?",
    "time": "2026-05-24T10:45:15"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dave",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Late‑night CS:GO session starting in 10. You in?",
    "time": "2026-05-24T17:15:02"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Do you think our router‑VPN is enough, or should we go full‑tunnel?",
    "time": "2026-05-24T00:34:57"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey Sarah, can you swing by the bakery tomorrow and grab the vanilla cake? Trying to keep the wedding timeline on track. 🙏",
    "time": "2026-05-26T20:04:27"
   },
   {
    "with": "NullRoute",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "NullRoute, can you give the latest prod logs a quick glance? Something's spiking and I don't want the alert to blow up in the morning.",
    "time": "2026-05-27T20:35:55"
   },
   {
    "with": "Jessica",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey Jess, any chance you could watch Barnaby this Saturday? He’s got a vet appointment Monday and I’ll be swamped with the final wedding checklist.",
    "time": "2026-05-28T20:09:52"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Sarah, Barnaby’s been acting off today—no appetite and a slight cough. I think we should book the vet ASAP. Feeling a bit panicked.",
    "time": "2026-05-29T12:39:43"
   },
   {
    "with": "Jessica",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Jessica, just got the prescription from the vet—Barnaby’s on antibiotics for the next 7 days. I’ll drop off the meds at your place if that works.",
    "time": "2026-05-29T13:54:08"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Barnaby’s back to his goofy self, thanks for the support. Heading to bed now—good night!",
    "time": "2026-05-30T20:16:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Jessica",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Hey Jess, Barnaby slipped and cut his paw. I need to get him to the vet later—can you help coordinate? Trying not to let it ruin the pre‑wedding vibe.",
    "time": "2026-06-01T13:49:18"
   }
